    "extras": [
      "Visa and Mastercard contactless cards work directly on MRT gates and buses, so you can skip EZ-Link unless you prefer a separate transit balance.",
      "Pre-book Marina Bay Sands SkyPark, Gardens by the Bay conservatories, and Sentosa attractions on Klook because timed slots and discounted inventory disappear on weekends and school holidays.",
      "Lau Pa Sat, Maxwell Food Centre, Tekka Centre, and Satay by the Bay keep many meals in the ₹250–₹600 range, which is the easiest way to keep Singapore costs under control.",
      "Use NEA myENV before outdoor blocks like Sentosa beaches, Botanic Gardens, or Supertree Grove because short tropical rain bursts can force same-day reordering.",
      "Little India is the easiest district for pure-vegetarian and Jain-friendly food; ask for no onion and no garlic when needed because staff hear that request often.",
      "If you want to save on Sentosa access, walk in via the boardwalk and only pay for attractions inside the island."
